---
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import Photo from "../assets/photo.png";
---

<section id="about" class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 bg-black">
	<div class="max-w-full mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
		<div class="mb-8 lg:mb-12">
			<h2
				class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-3 w-full lg:w-1/3"
			>
				ABOUT MAITEE
			</h2>
			<p class="text-small-circle text-sm md:text-base lg:text-lg">
				FROM STO. DOMINGO - OFERRING GREAT UI/UX EXPERIENCES
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-6 lg:gap-8">
			<Image
				class="w-full lg:w-1/2 object-cover rounded-2xl h-64 md:h-80 lg:h-auto"
				loading="lazy"
				src={Photo}
				alt="A photo of Maitee Batista smiling gently, dressed in a white tie-front shirt and a circular necklace, seated at a wooden table on a softly lit terrace in the evening."
			/>
			<div
				class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl xl:text-2xl flex flex-col gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:gap-12"
			>
				<div>
					<h4
						class="font-bold mb-4 md:mb-6 text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl"
					>
						ABOUT ME
					</h4>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						As a designer, my vision spans the entire creative
						spectrum. I'm dedicated to bringing projects to life
						that not only look exceptional but also achieve their
						strategic objectives. With a deep understanding of how
						design influences perception and interaction, I strive
						to create work that creates a meaningful impact and
						leaves a lasting mark.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h4
						class="mb-4 md:mb-6 font-bold text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl"
					>
						CERTIFICATIONS
					</h4>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 md:pl-8 space-y-2">
						<li>Web Assistant</li>
						<li>UX Design: UX/UI User Experience + Figma 2024</li>
						<li>User Experience (UX) Designer</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div>
					<h4
						class="mb-4 md:mb-6 font-bold text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-2xl"
					>
						MY MISION
					</h4>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						As a designer, my mission is to deliver excellence in
						every project, blending creativity with strategy. I
						constantly seek to innovate and refine so that each
						design not only fulfills its functional purpose but also
						elevates the perception and value of what it represents.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
